data.description: Active Under Contract - Accepting Back Up Offers. Get into this home for as fitting Welcome to a truly exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that seamlessly blends modern living with a touch of elegance. As you step inside, the high ceilings immediately create an open atmosphere. They allow natural light to dance throughout the space. This home stands out not only for its comfortable living areas but also for its dash of individuality.The expansive living areas offer a perfect balance between relaxation and entertainment, providing ample space for unwinding after a long day or hosting memorable gatherings with loved ones. The high ceilings not only enhance the visual appeal but also contribute to an overall sense of spaciousness that is both inviting and refreshing.What truly distinguishes this home is its one-of-a-kind layout that deviates from the norm in the neighborhood. This exceptional design lends character and uniqueness, ensuring that your living experience here is truly unparalleled. With each corner thoughtfully planned, this home maximizes both functionality and aesthetics. The space a harmonious fusion of form and function. A delightful tile back porch extends the living space outdoors. A cozy spot to enjoy your morning coffee or relax as the sun sets.From the open living areas to the meticulously designed bedrooms, this home offers a seamless blend of both modern living and architectural distinctiveness. Don't miss the opportunity to own this extraordinary 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that boasts high ceilings, a unique layout, a charming tile back porch, as well as a practical two-car garage. Experience the allure of this home firsthand and discover the comfort, character, and conveniences it has to offer.
